-- 2012-07-06T05:43:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-06/pgnig-seeks-foreign-partner-to-explore-shale-gas-dziennik-says.html
Polskie Gornictwo Naftowe i
Gazownictwo SA ,  Poland ’s dominant gas distributor, is in talks
with the world’s leading refiners to cooperate on shale gas
exploration in Poland, PGNiG Chief Executive Officer Grazyna Piotrowska-Oliwa told  Dziennik Gazeta Prawna , without
identifying any of the companies involved.  To contact the reporter on this story:
